n Uguk started running around while I was trying to get the mob off him, seconds later i'm running for the zone while hes dieing from pulling three rooms of frogs.  Ended up schooling him for a few hours so he won't wizz off another group, of course now hes back to outdoor kiting, go figure. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/umystykal.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mystykal</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 33<br> <font color=#333333>(7/21/01 12:15:55 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why solo</span><hr size=1> Because for a lot of people, the real fun starts post 50. <p><img src=http://www.caronetguay.qc.ca/nadine/mystykal.gif>
